ont-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>14 січня &ndash; субота</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Обрізання ГНІХ, св. Василія Великого</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">08:00 - Утреня, Літургія Василія Великого. <strong>2-га наука.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">18:00 - Велика вечірня. <strong>3-тя наука.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\