ca,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Надвечір\'я Богоявлення</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">08.00 &ndash; Царські часи, Вечірня з Літургією Василя Великого</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">17.00 &ndash; Велике Повечір\'я, Велике Водосвяття</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>19 січня &ndash; четвер</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Святе Богоявлення</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">08.00 &ndash; Утреня</span></