,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5399.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5398.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5452.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5455.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><br /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Презентація мультфільму <a href=\"item,4208\">&laquo;Велика історія маленької церкви&raquo;</a></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5423.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5431.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5422.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4213,200,CRW_5443.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>